            <description><![CDATA[【她有艾滋，生下健康宝宝！她有乙肝，却“遗传”给了娃<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[单身狗]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/co_niuec-7d05bc992a.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】就是这么不可思议，虽然中国是“乙肝大国”，但在吃瓜群众眼里，艾滋怎么也比乙肝可怕吧，但为什么感染了HIV的人能生出健康宝宝？而一个乙肝病毒携带者却没有这个“福分”？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[苦涩]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/7e/2021_bitter_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>阿卫提醒，深圳这些医院和社康中心，都可以筛查HIV、梅毒、乙肝👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫科普故事汇#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hi5dv3hi4fj20g918xacc.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hi5dv5eyt1j20u09rz1kx.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hi5dv5hz0nj20u05rr7nd.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hi5dv506c7j20u06f94jt.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hi5dv4qc34j20u069jdzq.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
